<font size="4">Round 1: Ohio State linebacker Ryan Shazier</font><br />
<font size="4">An ultra-athletic run-and-hit defensive player who will likely start in Week 1 opposite Lawrence Timmons</font>.<br />
<br />
Yes, and we draft A SECOND LBer before addressing the &quot;ever so pressing need&quot; at the NT in the sixth round. <img src="images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="" class="inlineimg" />
